# Google News Template API (v1.0.0)

Google News Template API is an API which allows consumers to interact with sample news content.

# Root [/]

## Status Check [GET]

This action allows consumers to verify the status of the server. A response status code `204` indicates that the server is healthy.

+ Response 204 (application/json)

## Headlines [/api/v1/headlines{?category,limit,page}]

Resources related to top headlines.

+ Parameters
    + category (optional, enum[string]) - The headline category.
        + Default: general
        + Members            
            + business
            + entertainment
            + general
            + health
            + science
            + sports
            + technology
    + limit (optional, number) - The number of articles to return.
        + Default: 20
    + page (optional, number) - The page of results to return.
        + Default: 0

### Get Headlines [GET]

This action allows you to query top headlines.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + articles (required, array[Article]) - The list of articles.
        + next (optional, string) - The URL for the next batch of articles if available.

