# Data Structures

## Article (object)

+ author (required, string) - the author of the article
+ category (required, string) - the category of the article
+ content (required, string) - a preview of the article content
+ description (required, string) - a short description of the article
+ image_url (required, string) - the URL of the image associated with the article
+ published_at (required, string) - the timestamp of when the article was published (ISO8601)
+ title (required, string) - the title of the article
+ url (required, string) - the URL of the full article